"metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/2009-global-assessment-report-disaster-risk-reduction-%E2%80%93-risk-and-poverty-changing-climate", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "2009 Global Assessment Report on Disaster Risk Reduction \u2013 Risk and poverty in a changing climate", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/2009-global-assessment-report-disaster-risk-reduction-%E2%80%93-risk-and-poverty-changing-climate", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "16a947a75e6f3a822281a54a62bcb4042f9d3f6e11d59c7bd9d770ae40b338c2"}, "2": {"node_id": "e580fcd1-08d5-40a0-bdf3-9871574f3258", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/2009-global-assessment-report-disaster-risk-reduction-%E2%80%93-risk-and-poverty-changing-climate", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "ac337e884a0fd0e4335b29334a3c2b24df2b684a02bce4de450bc4988d25e9cc"}}, "hash": "b8feacc7ce46a06838baf678901ba4cc9011df2855551670f8618d07dee350df", "text": "The following organisations, among others, have provided substantive inputs to the Report\u2019s analysis. To access the 2009 Global Assessment Report on Disaster Risk Reduction and related materials online, log onto: www.preventionweb.net/gar09 Summary and Recommendations: 2009 Global Assessment Report on Disaster Risk Reduction Risk and poverty in a changing climate Invest today for a safer tomorrow United Nations Contents Introduction 3 Key findings and recommendations 3 A 20-point plan to reduce risk 5 Global disaster risk: the challenge 6 Disaster risk an